  <Content>Alsaids is currently in the testing phase and will be released at the end of March. Besides the quests, hunting areas, and some items there will also be a few additional features.

Combo Skill - Druids will be given the combo skill. A combo skill will allow players to set an order of moves using their current skills. Pure Druids will get 3 moves for their combo skill while Sub Druids will get 2 moves. When using the combo skill, the moves will execute in the order they were set. Each move will use 1500 mana. There is a 2 minute cooldown after the completion of a combo.

